title: ACS Icon Catalogue
content:
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:toggle-sidebar-bhl]]

[[include :scp-wiki:info:start]]
**Compiler:** [[*user hakr14]]
[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]

There are quite a few [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/esoteric-classes-complete-list esoteric classes] across the several canons of the Foundation. Some have icons for use with the [http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:anomaly-class-bar ACS], some don't. In the interest of uniformity, here is a compiled list of all icons known to be in use for all esoteric classes.
When multiple icons are known, they are shown in order of most to least used. When two or more icons are used the same amount, they are instead shown in order of date of first known use.

[[div style="border: solid 1px #000000; background: #f2f2c2; margin: 10px 5px; padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;"]]
++++* This is an open, collaborative project. If you discover a class or icon that is absent or has been improperly cataloged, feel free to add it.
[[/div]]

[[module CSS]]
.acs-icon {
    width: 35px;
    border: 0.1875rem solid rgb(12, 12, 12);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);
}
[[/module]]
